✅ Plugin Folder Structure
elementor-custom-widgets/
├── elementor-custom-widgets.php
├── assets/
│   └── css/
│       └── custom-widgets.css
├── widgets/
│   ├── cta-box-widget.php
│   └── testimonial-widget.php


✅ 1. Main Plugin File – elementor-custom-widgets.php
✅ 2. CSS File – assets/css/custom-widgets.css
✅ 3. CTA Box Widget – widgets/cta-box-widget.php
✅ 4. Testimonial Widget – widgets/testimonial-widget.php


✅ You can now go to Elementor → Search for “CTA Box” or “Testimonial Box” and add them to your page.
🎨 The custom CSS will automatically apply the styling.
